<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊闻到薄饼味，醒了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈在做薄饼吗？” 乔伊想，那可不常见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊冲向楼下。“爷爷！” 她喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷在燃气灶前翻着薄饼。“谁想吃薄饼？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊给了爷爷一个大大的拥抱。“您什么时候回来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天一大早。你爸爸和我天一亮就开车直接回来了。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说你为了写完学校作业，做到很晚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊咧嘴笑了。“是的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我写完了关于领袖的发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我准备好吃薄饼和玩儿雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，凯蒂跑进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，爸爸拿着柴火从后门走了进来，妈妈跟着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！爷爷！” 凯蒂惊讶地喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我等不及想听你们讲周末的事情了。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他调皮地拽了一下凯蒂的马尾辫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们又团聚了，很开心吧？” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷在桌子上放了一大盘薄饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，爷爷回来给我们做早饭，很开心吧？” 凯蒂回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对了，我们不在家时，有什么新鲜事吗？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对妈妈眨了一下眼，“除了凉麦片和烤糊的布朗尼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，外面特别冷。” 凯蒂开始说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以为有小偷偷了鸡蛋和母鸡！” 乔伊补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，其实是母鸡们从栅栏的一个洞逃了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们还在落叶堆上下了蛋。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇啊！” 爷爷惊讶地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还好不是遇到了真正的小偷。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“后来，乔伊一个人修好了栅栏上的洞。” 凯蒂边吃薄饼边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真棒！” 爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，我们明天终于要在学校发表了。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你最后选了谁？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈丽特·塔布曼，” 乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她奉献了自己的一生做了一件重要的事情——让奴隶们获得自由。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的选择很好！” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 乔伊把枫糖浆倒在薄饼上，想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会成为哈丽特·塔布曼那样的伟大领袖吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，” 乔伊慢慢地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你小的时候，长大了想做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸笑了，“我想在公园里工作，照顾树木。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你帮助大家回收废物的同时，不也在照顾树木嘛！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸笑了，“算是吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，您呢？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷在柳树溪做了30年的邮递员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从我九岁起，就想当一个邮递员了。” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢看人们收到特别信件或包裹时的微笑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直想当一个图书管理员。” 妈妈紧接着说，“你们呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要当柳树溪的市长！” 凯蒂大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸笑了，“那很适合你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊也开心地笑了。“我想当一个兽医。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些工作都很棒，” 爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为都是帮助别人的事，就像领袖们一样，也和你们俩做的一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>双胞胎看着对方笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，姐姐，” 凯蒂说，“你吃完薄饼了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，吃完了。” 乔伊回答说，“我们该去玩儿雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂已经站在门口了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接着！” 说着，她把乔伊的靴子扔了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊笑着接住了靴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，她希望自己有个姐姐；</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，她希望自己有个妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但今天，她为自己和凯蒂是双胞胎，而感到开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是一对双胞胎，很有意思吧？” 乔伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 凯蒂回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时候，做你的双胞胎姐妹，才会更有意思哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就这样，柳树溪双胞胎姐妹一起冲进了雪地里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>